(142, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/sal-fragale/', 'Verizon', 'Senior Engineering Manager, Emerging Technology & Application Security', '', 'As a Senior Manager for Sales & Service applications, I led a team of savvy developers responsible for various emerging technology solutions such as robotic process automation, enterprise search, conversational chatbots, and streaming analytics.  In addition, my team was responsible for application security and compliance for 140 applications.  Most notably introduced a new program to ingest real-time data points from 50+ systems to create a personalized shopping experience while customers interact with Verizon in any channel.   In addition, we designed a smart algorithm to pin-point network opportunities proactively based upon real-time customer sentiment and speech analytics.As a Senior Manager for Sales & Service applications, I led a team of savvy developers responsible for various emerging technology solutions such as robotic process automation, enterprise search, conversational chatbots, and streaming analytics.  In addition, my team was responsible for application security and compliance for 140 applications.  Most notably introduced a new program to ingest real-time data points from 50+ systems to create a personalized shopping experience while customers interact with Verizon in any channel.   In addition, we designed a smart algorithm to pin-point network opportunities proactively based upon real-time customer sentiment and speech analytics.', '2017 - 2019', '2 yrs', 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C560BAQHAiVb75wIpDQ/company-logo_100_100/0/1645721743189/verizon_logo?e=1727308800&v=beta&t=5YE9MbPjk4M0Rxy0IZRUaAoG-LLKy9GUigfsdepK-1c'),
