(150, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/pranay-bajpai-470246/', 'Verizon', 'Systems Engineer, Network Activation & Provisioning', '', 'Provisioning & Activation PlatformsDeveloped & implemented provisioning & activation workflows for DSL (Digital Subscriber Line), Fast Packet ATM (Asynchronous Transfer Mode) and Frame Relay services. Tools developed to automate Verizon’s ability to provision and activate DSL service subscribers using DSLAM (Digital Subscriber Line Access Managers) and PVC (Permanent Virtual Circuits). The tools also enabled Verizon to migrate from Level 3 (L3) communications IP backbone network to its own IP backbone.Provisioning & Activation Platforms\n\nDeveloped & implemented provisioning & activation workflows for DSL (Digital Subscriber Line), Fast Packet ATM (Asynchronous Transfer Mode) and Frame Relay services. Tools developed to automate Verizon’s ability to provision and activate DSL service subscribers using DSLAM (Digital Subscriber Line Access Managers) and PVC (Permanent Virtual Circuits). The tools also enabled Verizon to migrate from Level 3 (L3) communications IP backbone network to its own IP backbone.', 'May 2003 - Aug 2005', '2 yrs 4 mos', 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C560BAQHAiVb75wIpDQ/company-logo_100_100/0/1645721743189/verizon_logo?e=1727308800&v=beta&t=5YE9MbPjk4M0Rxy0IZRUaAoG-LLKy9GUigfsdepK-1c'),
